Declaring nodes and manipulating pointer links in C++:

```cpp
struct FListNode {
    int Data;
    FListNode* Next = nullptr;

    FListNode(int InVal) : Data(InVal) {}
};

void InsertNode(FListNode* Head, int NewVal) {
    FListNode* NewNode = new FListNode(NewVal);
    // Insert right after head
    NewNode->Next = Head->Next;
    Head->Next = NewNode;
}
```
